fields.value: Replication data for: Southern Politics Project

dsDescriptionValue.value: The Southern Politics Project offers precinct election data from the general election for Alabama, Arkansas, Florida, Georgia, Louisiana, Mississippi, North Carolina, South Carolina, Tennessee and Virginia from 1984 to 1990. The site works in conjunction with the ROAD project in collecting and posting this data.

publicationCitation.value: David Lublin. 2007. "Southern Politics Projects." (in progress). project available here
